# MusicPlayer.Queue.Entry.Item

**Enumeration**

An item that corresponds to an entry in the playback queue.

## Declaration

```swift
enum Item
```

## Enumeration Cases

- **MusicPlayer.Queue.Entry.Item.musicVideo(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a music video.
- **MusicPlayer.Queue.Entry.Item.song(_:)**: An item that corresponds to a song.

## Instance Properties

- **id**: The unique identifier for the music player item.
- **playParameters**: The parameters to use to play the item.
